Definition: thinking that moves away in diverging directions so as to involve a variety of aspects and which sometimes lead to novel ideas and solutions
Example: associated with creativity
Synonyms: convergent_thinking, out-of-the-box_thinking, thinking, creativity, p, that, moves, away, in, diverging, directions, so, as, to, involve, a, variety, of, aspects, and, which, sometimes, lead, novel, ideas, solutions, associated, with
Category: noun.cognition
